parameters:
I kind of thought it would be nice to live a peaceful life
like this.

\SE[13] Alright... Today's progress is all good now...!
\SE[1] Yeah yeah... You're doing great!

\SE[2] After this, let's take care of the flowers... Let's
make Lunaroa-sama look beautiful... \SE[0] And then, maybe
we can take a little break...

\SE[12] Cactus-chan... You're just too low-maintenance, it's
boring... \SE[38] I don't feel any sense of accomplishment
at all...

\SE[14] In comparison, you are so demanding...! You're too
neurotic about the amount of water and nutrients...! \SE[37]
With such selfishness, it's impressive that you've managed
to survive in this harsh competition for survival...!

\SE[6]But, growing up so beautifully... \SE[36]It's true
that the more demanding they are, the cuter they become...

\SE[11] Looking good! Lunaroa-sama...! \SE[10] In another 10
years, you'll become a giant tree that pierces the heavens!
I'm sure you'll be delighted...!! \SE[14] You seem to like
big things, don't you...!

\SE[0]... Lunaroa-sama. \ Just a little more... \ is what it
is. \! \SE[0] Laura and the others should be coming back.

\SE[30] Everyone worked so hard. Please... show me your
smiles again. \SE[46] Especially to Laura... the most
dazzling one...

\SE[37] That girl... I was so worried she might break... I
did my best for Lunaroa-sama. \SE[1] So... please, praise
her a lot.

\SE[10] I'm 'okay'...! \!\SE[21] It would be a lie to say
that it wasn't tough.... \!\SE[0] But more than that, I feel
like I'm able to be of use...!

\SE[47] Deep down in my heart, I... \SE[38] secretly wished
that Lunaroa-sama would never wake up. \SE[37] I wished that
this moment could last forever...

\SE[52] Your smile when you woke up... it's surely directed
towards Laura and not towards me... \SE[53]... That's what
really scares me.

\SE[44] I'm the worst...! \SE[53] I only think about
myself...! \SE[52] Hoping that you wouldn't wake up...
That's impossible...!
\SE[2]So this is... my selfishness, at least to some extent.

If it's just a 'cheek'... \. Will you forgive me... \.
Lunaroa- sama...?

Lunaroa-sama... Thank you very much. And, goodbye. My first
love...

It seems to be called a 'life support system.' It appears to
provide the body with necessary nutrients and oxygen.
However, I'm not quite sure about the exact mechanism.
